    <item>
      <title>特朗普对哥伦比亚发动 9 小时经济战 震惊新兴市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/trump-s-9-hour-economic-war-on-colombia-rattles-emerging-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自唐纳德·特朗普上任以来，哥伦比亚大部分时间都远离他的视线。特朗普专注于墨西哥和中国等国，几乎对哥伦比亚只字未提，这让波哥大的交易员有信心稳步推高比索和股价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/trump-s-9-hour-economic-war-on-colombia-rattles-emerging-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
