      <title>美联储会议纪要：纳斯达克期货上涨，科技股在美联储会议前反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员将注意力转向大型科技公司的收益和美联储的利率决定，美国股指期货上涨，延续了本周初从人工智能引发的暴跌中复苏的势头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 22:41:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储决策前押注美国国债大幅上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/bets-on-bigger-treasuries-rally-are-booming-before-fed-decision</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储公布利率决定前，美国国债维持近期涨幅，因交易员加大看涨押注，希望美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔将暗示 3 月份降息是板上钉钉的事。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/bets-on-bigger-treasuries-rally-are-booming-before-fed-decision</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 21:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
